ay">Coldplay</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA 等</a>音乐人的音乐表演，还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shania-twain-talks-glastonbury-2024-legends-slot-honour-of-my-life-3600979">仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain) 的传奇老虎机</a>表演以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lcd-soundsystem">LCD Soundsystem</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pj-harvey">PJ Harvey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/burna-boy">Burna</a>的表演。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/burna-boy">Boy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idles">Idles</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anne-marie">Anne-Marie</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/confidence-man">Confidence Man</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/disclosure">Disclosure</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/camila-cabello">Camila Cabello</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">Avril Lavigne</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jessie-ware">Jessie Ware</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jungle">Jungle</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justice">Justice</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/masego">Masego</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sugababes">Sugababes</a>等等。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-set-times-stage-splits-3749871">在这里查看完整的阵容。</a></p><p>与此同时，<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/glastonbury-2024-set-clash-guide-3766391">以下是今年预计最严重的冲突</a>，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-weather-forecast-3763664">2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的最新天气预报</a>。</p><p><em><a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">请访问此处，</a>了解 Glastonbury 2024 的所有最新新闻、评论、照片、采访等。</em></p><p></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-bombay-bicycle-club-rumoured-to-be-b